# Commonality and Variability Analysis

## Commonalities
- Messages live in batches.
- Messages can be sent and recieved.

## Variabilities
- Deleting and editing messages.
  - Why it may change    User's may want to be able to fix errors or retype certain parts of their messages, or remove them altogether.
  - How it is isolated : Bridge dispatching is event based and new constants can be made to accomodate specific operations on messages.

